sql:
SELECT file_path
FROM size_chart_documents
WHERE size_chart_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "voyagers exploring the uncharted territories" metaphorically represents users who have left comments on a size chart;
- "size chart 0" refers to the specific size chart with an identifier of 0;
- "revealing their full profiles" means selecting all information about these users.

sql:
SELECT comment_text
FROM size_chart_comments
WHERE size_chart_id = 1 AND comment_text = 'Checked measurements for accuracy';

SELECT sc.chart_name, cc.category_name
FROM size_charts sc
INNER JOIN clothing_categories cc ON sc.category_id = cc.category_id;

external_knowledge:
- 'vibrant voices in the comment section' refers to users who leave multiple comments;
- 'sown more than a handful of seeds of discussion' implies users who have commented more than 10 times;
- 'reveal their identities' means to provide the names and emails of these users;
- 'depth of their contributions' indicates the number of comments each user has made.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT T1.brand_name
FROM brands AS T1
INNER JOIN size_charts AS T2 ON T1.brand_id = T2.brand_id;
